data: {"type":"response.output_text.done","sequence_number":317,"item_id":"msg_eb1bdff9108d64b20069337754985c819082a4a4a0d86a4d4b","output_index":1,"content_index":0,"text":"Contoso products, specifically from the Contoso Galaxy Innovations brand, include a category known as Smart Eyewear, which is part of their innovative line. Here's a detailed look at their features:\n\n### Features of Smart Eyewear:\n1. **Augmented Reality Interface**: This feature allows users to experience augmented reality through the eyewear, providing immersive visualizations directly on the lenses.\n   \n2. **Voice-controlled AI Agent**: The product integrates an AI agent that responds to voice commands, enhancing hands-free control and functionality.\n\n3. **HD Video Recording with 3D Audio**: Users can capture high-definition videos complemented by 3D audio, delivering a rich multimedia experience.\n\n4. **UV Protection and Blue Light Filtering**: The eyewear includes protective measures against UV rays and filters blue light, safeguarding the user's eyes in various lighting conditions.\n\n5. **Wireless Charging and Extended Battery Life**: It supports wireless charging, making it convenient to maintain power, and features an extended battery life for prolonged use.\n\n### Additional Information:\n- **Warranty**: Contoso offers a two-year limited warranty on all electronic components.\n  \n- **Return Policy**: There is a 30-day return policy with no questions asked.\n\n- **User Guide**: The product comes with a comprehensive user guide covering introduction, product overview, sizing, care, maintenance, and troubleshooting.\n\nThese detailed features make Contoso's Smart Eyewear a versatile and technologically advanced option for users looking to integrate smart technology into their daily lives.","logprobs":[]}

