data: {"type":"response.output_text.done","sequence_number":252,"item_id":"msg_eb1bdff9108d64b20069337759d360819090d473cf211c1262","output_index":1,"content_index":0,"text":"Contoso's Smart Eyewear, branded under Contoso Galaxy Innovations, includes several advanced features that make it a standout product in the category. Here's a detailed overview:\n\n### Features of Smart Eyewear:\n\n- **Augmented Reality Interface**: The eyewear provides an immersive augmented reality experience directly on its lenses.\n  \n- **Voice-controlled AI Agent**: Integrated AI responds to voice commands, enabling hands-free operation.\n  \n- **HD Video Recording with 3D Audio**: Users have the ability to record high-definition video combined with 3D audio for enhanced media creation.\n\n- **UV Protection and Blue Light Filtering**: The eyewear includes features for eye protection against UV rays and reduces blue light exposure.\n\n- **Wireless Charging and Extended Battery Life**: It supports wireless charging, providing convenience, and is designed for prolonged usage due to its extended battery life.\n\n### Additional Information:\n\n- **Warranty**: A two-year limited warranty is included for all electronic components.\n  \n- **Return Policy**: There is a 30-day return policy, allowing returns without any questions asked.\n\nThese features make Smart Eyewear a versatile and technologically-rich product, enhancing both functionality and user experience.","logprobs":[]}

